---
---

<footer class="mt-7 border border-[rgba(248,242,235,0.08)] rounded-3xl lg:rounded-[34px] bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,#1a1b1f,#101114)] shadow-[var(--shadow-sm)] text-[color:var(--color-paper-strong)] p-[22px] lg:p-[clamp(28px,4vw,44px)]" id="laboratorio">
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1.3fr)_minmax(0,0.7fr)] gap-5">
    <div>
      <p class="mb-3.5 text-[rgba(248,242,235,0.58)] font-[family-name:var(--font-archivo)] text-[0.76rem] leading-none tracking-[0.16em] uppercase">Laboratorio</p>
      <h2 class="m-0 font-[family-name:var(--font-archivo)] font-semibold text-[clamp(2.4rem,13vw,3.8rem)] lg:text-[clamp(2.3rem,5.4vw,4.8rem)] leading-[0.96] tracking-[-0.06em] max-w-[11ch]">Hackear la imagen. Defender el montaje.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="grid content-start gap-3.5 p-[22px] rounded-[20px] lg:rounded-[var(--radius-lg)] border border-[rgba(248,242,235,0.08)] bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top_right,rgba(189,58,51,0.18),transparent_28%),rgba(248,242,235,0.04)]">
      <p class="m-0 text-[rgba(248,242,235,0.8)] text-base leading-[1.7]">
        Cineastas, artistas, técnicos y libre pensadores leyendo la imagen desde Latinoamérica.
      </p>
      <p class="m-0 text-[rgba(248,242,235,0.8)] text-base leading-[1.7]">
        Cine, teoría crítica, archivo, software e IA sin obediencia al sistema cultural dominante.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-7">
    <article class="footer-column min-h-[170px] grid content-start gap-3 p-[22px] rounded-[20px] lg:rounded-[var(--radius-lg)] border border-[rgba(248,242,235,0.08)] bg-[rgba(248,242,235,0.04)]">
      <span class="text-[rgba(248,242,235,0.56)] font-[family-name:var(--font-archivo)] text-[0.76rem] leading-none tracking-[0.16em] uppercase">Base</span>
      <p class="m-0 text-[rgba(248,242,235,0.78)] leading-[1.7]">cine / teoría de la imagen / archivo / montaje</p>
    </article>
    <article class="footer-column min-h-[170px] grid content-start gap-3 p-[22px] rounded-[20px] lg:rounded-[var(--radius-lg)] border border-[rgba(248,242,235,0.08)] bg-[rgba(248,242,235,0.04)]">
      <span class="text-[rgba(248,242,235,0.56)] font-[family-name:var(--font-archivo)] text-[0.76rem] leading-none tracking-[0.16em] uppercase">Práctica</span>
      <p class="m-0 text-[rgba(248,242,235,0.78)] leading-[1.7]">piezas / ensayos / cuadernos / sistemas editoriales</p>
    </article>
  </div>

  <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center justify-between gap-4 mt-7 pt-[18px] border-t border-[rgba(248,242,235,0.08)]">
    <strong class="font-[family-name:var(--font-archivo)] text-[1.3rem] leading-none tracking-[-0.04em]">CineIndustria</strong>
    <span class="text-[rgba(248,242,235,0.58)] text-[0.78rem] tracking-[0.16em] uppercase">señal en desarrollo &bull; online</span>
  </div>
</footer>
